** command for setting defaults in azure cli, in order to no more write the location and resource-group**
az configure --defaults location=northeurope group=rg-rbr-webapp

** command for creating a web app **
dotnet new webapi -n "WebApiInAppService" --no-openapi

** command to see the runtimes needed for setting in Web App creation **
az webapp list-runtimes --os-type linux

** Creates a service principal with 'contributor' rights scoped to the resource group. **
The output is a JSON object that will be used as the authentication secret.
```
az ad sp create-for-rbac --name "github-actions-az204" --role "contributor" --scopes "/subscriptions/{subscription_id}/resourceGroups/rg-rbr-webapp-cicd" --sdk-auth
```